    "description": {
      "value": "<div><div><p>Upon reaching 20th level, you manifest a spark of divine power in defense of the mortal realms. As a bonus action, you gain the following benefits for 1 hour:</p><ul><li>You gain truesight with a range of 120 feet.</li><li>You have advantage on attack rolls against aberrations, celestials, elementals, fey, and fiends.</li><li>When you hit a creature with an attack roll and deal damage to it, you can also force it to make a Charisma saving throw against your spell save DC. On a failed save, the creature is magically banished to its native plane of existence if it's currently not there. On a successful save, the creature cannot be banished by this feature for 24 hours.</li></ul></div></div><div><div><p>Once you use this bonus action, you cannot use it again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a 5th-level spell slot to use it again.</p></div></div>",
